Strategic Value Partners, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 23, 2017 8:23 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Strategic Value Partners, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Strategic Value Partners, LLC is a privately owned investment manager. The firm manages hedge funds and private equity funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity markets, alternative investment markets, and private equity markets across the globe. The firm also invests in the real estate markets. It employs a combination of distressed and deep value investment strategies and focuses on turnaround opportunities to create its portfolio. Strategic Value Partners, LLC was founded in 2001 and is based in Greenwich, Connecticut with additional offices in London, United Kingdom; Frankfurt, Germany; Tokyo, Japan, and Luxembourg.


